'''''Boldheart''''' was a [[Corona-class frigate|''Corona''-class frigate]] of the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]].

==History==
While on patrol during [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Natasi Daala|Daala's]] campaign in [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], ''Boldheart'' came across the ''[[Teljkon Vagabond]]''&mdash;the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] first encounter with the vessel. When ''Boldheart'' attempted to halt the vessel with a shot across its bow, the Vagabond disabled the frigate's engines with a single shot and fled into [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]]. The holos from this encounter provided [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]] with its first images of the ''Vagabond''.

